## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5950d-103">使用<xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute>屬性來標記靜態值型別，因為在建立時固定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-103">Use the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute> attribute to mark static value types as pinned upon creation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5950d-104">Microsoft Visual c + + 編譯器會使用這個屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-104">This attribute is used by the Microsoft Visual C++ compiler.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5950d-105">靜態值類型欄位會建立為 boxed 物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-105">Static value type fields are created as boxed objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-106">這表示執行記憶體回收時，可以變更其位址。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-106">This means that their address can change as garbage collection is performed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-107">當您套用這個屬性為靜態值型別時，它的位址會維持不變在其存留期間。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-107">When you apply this attribute to a static value type, its address remains constant during its lifetime.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5950d-108">下列範例示範如何將<xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute>釘選在記憶體中的靜態欄位的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-108">The following example illustrates the use of the <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute> attribute to pin a static field in memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-109">它會定義`Age`結構，並初始化具有類型的靜態欄位的兩個類別`Age`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-109">It defines an `Age` structure and initializes two classes that have static fields of type `Age`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-110">第二個類別適用於<xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute>釘選欄位的位址。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-110">The second class applies <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute> to pin the field's address.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-111">之前和之後這兩個物件會具現化，並叫用記憶體回收行程進行記憶體配置數目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-111">A number of memory allocations are made before and after these two objects are instantiated and the garbage collector is invoked.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5950d-112">範例輸出顯示，但第一個地址`Age`欄位已變更廢棄項目收集至欄位的位址之後<xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute>套用尚未。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5950d-112">The output from the example shows that although the address of the first `Age` field has changed after garbage collection, the address of the field to which <xref:System.Runtime.CompilerServices.FixedAddressValueTypeAttribute> is applied has not.</span></span>  
  
